One has a great idea for a surprise!
Preparing in secret will add to the gift.

The crown is ready to be shown off...
But no! The wind caught it just right...

Aha! A floral coronation ensues.
That smile is prettier than any flower!

Aww... They both had the same idea!
Birds flit happily as the two celebrate.

A massive cake baked to celebrate the
eighth anniversary. It's an event item.

Used in Aether Raids to build structures that
are available for a limited time. If that period
has elapsed, these stones will be lost.
